    <briefdescription>
<para>Network Management event information structure Used to pass information on network event NET_EVENT_VPN_PEER_ADD when CONFIG_NET_MGMT_EVENT_INFO enabled and event generator pass the information. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The network event NET_EVENT_VPN_PEER_DEL will pass the peer id only as a pointer in the event info. Note that the pointers to the peer information are only valid during the event handling and should not be used after the event is processed. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
